1
00:00:01,169 --> 00:00:04,379
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:08,720 --> 00:00:09,920
<Default><b>[straining]</b></Default>

3
00:00:10,599 --> 00:00:11,759
<Default><b>[shouting]</b></Default>

4
00:00:17,809 --> 00:00:19,190
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

5
00:00:24,609 --> 00:00:25,756
<Default><b>This isn't good.</b></Default>

6
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:27,580
<Default><b>I can't block
what's next!</b></Default>

7
00:00:28,949 --> 00:00:30,149
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

8
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:32,420
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Leave it to me!</b></Default>

9
00:00:37,659 --> 00:00:39,179
<Default><b>- [shouting]
- Atla!</b></Default>

10
00:00:43,090 --> 00:00:44,130
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

11
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,929
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

12
00:00:53,549 --> 00:00:54,969
<Default><b>Atla...</b></Default>

13
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:57,179
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

14
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,960
<Default><b>[water trickling]</b></Default>

15
00:01:02,350 --> 00:01:03,470
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

16
00:01:07,609 --> 00:01:09,249
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Stay with me.</b></Default>

17
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:46,855
<Default><b>[coughing]</b></Default>

18
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:49,199
<Default><b>I didn't know
you couldn't swim Sir Ren.</b></Default>

19
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,485
<Default><b>It's not one of
my strengths.</b></Default>

20
00:02:51,509 --> 00:02:52,629
<Default><b>[hissing]</b></Default>

21
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:55,090
<Default><b>Sorry, Atla,
was that painful?</b></Default>

22
00:02:55,219 --> 00:02:56,969
<Default><b>A little, but I'm okay.</b></Default>

23
00:02:57,139 --> 00:02:58,779
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Ow, that stings!</b></Default>

24
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:01,259
<Default><b>Stop whining.
It's not that bad.</b></Default>

25
00:03:01,349 --> 00:03:02,549
<Default><b>[squirming]</b></Default>

26
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:07,110
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

27
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,665
<Default><b>How's Filo?</b></Default>

28
00:03:08,689 --> 00:03:10,246
<Default><b>She's still
hanging in there</b></Default>

29
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:12,376
<Default><b>but her levels are
going down rapidly.</b></Default>

30
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,150
<Default><b>I see, that means...</b></Default>

31
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:16,216
<Default><b>We don't have
much time left.</b></Default>

32
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,080
<Default><b>Yeah, I think
you're right.</b></Default>

33
00:03:18,409 --> 00:03:19,756
<Default><b>By tomorrow morning</b></Default>

34
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:22,140
<Default><b>he'll have drained away
every last level.</b></Default>

35
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:24,385
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] The most effective
attack we've got right now</b></Default>

36
00:03:24,409 --> 00:03:27,210
<Default><b>is Atla's which scales off
the enemy's defense stat.</b></Default>

37
00:03:27,539 --> 00:03:28,539
<Default><b>But...</b></Default>

38
00:03:32,129 --> 00:03:33,169
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

39
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,526
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
How're you feeling?</b></Default>

40
00:03:36,550 --> 00:03:38,485
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Much better now, thanks.</b></Default>

41
00:03:38,509 --> 00:03:40,229
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
That's a relief.</b></Default>

42
00:03:40,349 --> 00:03:41,615
<Default><b>Oh, by the way</b></Default>

43
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:44,115
<Default><b>there's something I've been
meaning to ask you, Wyndia.</b></Default>

44
00:03:44,139 --> 00:03:45,246
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

45
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,939
<Default><b>I was just wondering</b></Default>

46
00:03:47,099 --> 00:03:49,859
<Default><b>is that giant dragon back
there really your father?</b></Default>

47
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,260
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

48
00:03:52,069 --> 00:03:53,150
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

49
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:55,450
<Default><b>He's the one
who raised me.</b></Default>

50
00:03:56,449 --> 00:03:57,569
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

51
00:04:04,789 --> 00:04:05,869
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

52
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:09,230
<Default><b>[birds fluttering]</b></Default>

53
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,220
<Default><b>I'm sorry</b></Default>

54
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:26,470
<Default><b>but can you watch over
my daughter?</b></Default>

55
00:04:27,019 --> 00:04:28,139
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

56
00:04:34,029 --> 00:04:35,269
<Default><b>I thank you.</b></Default>

57
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:39,029
<Default><b>My daughter's
name is... Wyndia.</b></Default>

58
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,819
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

59
00:04:45,410 --> 00:04:46,530
<Default><b>[hissing]</b></Default>

60
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,170
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

61
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,839
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

62
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,630
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

63
00:05:01,930 --> 00:05:03,050
<Default><b>[wailing]</b></Default>

64
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,060
<Default><b>[clattering]</b></Default>

65
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,759
<Default><b>[wailing]</b></Default>

66
00:05:15,819 --> 00:05:19,819
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

67
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:35,999
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

68
00:05:37,589 --> 00:05:38,709
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

69
00:05:40,379 --> 00:05:42,220
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

70
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,800
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

71
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:01,779
<Default><b>This is super yummy</b></Default>

72
00:06:09,490 --> 00:06:10,500
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

73
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,500
<Default><b>Why is this one
upside-down?</b></Default>

74
00:06:14,209 --> 00:06:15,329
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

75
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,396
<Default><b>[gasps]
Dad, what's wrong?</b></Default>

76
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,855
<Default><b>I'm sorry! I didn't know
that it would hurt you!</b></Default>

77
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:23,300
<Default><b>It was an accident! I promise
I didn't mean to do it, really!</b></Default>

78
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,889
<Default><b>That's right.
I'd almost forgot!</b></Default>

79
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:27,100
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

80
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,950
<Default><b>The upside-down scale.</b></Default>

81
00:06:29,139 --> 00:06:30,659
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

82
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:33,139
<Default><b>I have to go and tell the
Shield Hero!</b></Default>

83
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:36,586
<Default><b>This is a good ways
out from the village.</b></Default>

84
00:06:36,610 --> 00:06:38,415
<Default><b>If we can lure
the dragon here</b></Default>

85
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:40,359
<Default><b>we can attack
him from above.</b></Default>

86
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,586
<Default><b>Not only that</b></Default>

87
00:06:41,610 --> 00:06:43,970
<Default><b>the dragon vein is
especially strong here</b></Default>

88
00:06:44,029 --> 00:06:46,295
<Default><b>so we'll have the
protection of the land as well.</b></Default>

89
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:48,555
<Default><b>I think this is a great place
to fight him.</b></Default>

90
00:06:48,579 --> 00:06:50,939
<Default><b>But why would he
willingly come out here?</b></Default>

91
00:06:51,449 --> 00:06:53,409
<Default><b>I'm gonna use
the Wrath Shield.</b></Default>

92
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:56,709
<Default><b>No matter what it takes</b></Default>

93
00:06:57,339 --> 00:06:58,646
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Well then, everyone</b></Default>

94
00:06:58,670 --> 00:07:00,315
<Default><b>we better start
getting ready!</b></Default>

95
00:07:00,339 --> 00:07:01,855
<Default><b>[MELTY]
I'll hide all the magic water</b></Default>

96
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:04,599
<Default><b>and healing potions
that I can find in the forest.</b></Default>

97
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:05,855
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
We still need to repair</b></Default>

98
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,326
<Default><b>our weapons
and equipment.</b></Default>

99
00:07:07,350 --> 00:07:09,076
<Default><b>What's our attack
plan, though?</b></Default>

100
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:10,009
<Default><b>Well, for starters...</b></Default>

101
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:12,260
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
There you are, Shield Hero!</b></Default>

102
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,759
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

103
00:07:15,389 --> 00:07:18,019
<Default><b>Everyone, listen!
I figured it out!</b></Default>

104
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:19,670
<Default><b>I know its weakness!</b></Default>

105
00:07:23,189 --> 00:07:24,439
<Default><b>A scale?</b></Default>

106
00:07:24,779 --> 00:07:25,925
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

107
00:07:25,949 --> 00:07:27,789
<Default><b>One of the
dragon's scales.</b></Default>

108
00:07:27,819 --> 00:07:29,779
<Default><b>It's upside-down
on its chest.</b></Default>

109
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:31,966
<Default><b>That scale is the
dragon's weak spot.</b></Default>

110
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:33,310
<Default><b>Least I think.</b></Default>

111
00:07:33,370 --> 00:07:35,959
<Default><b>But what do we do
if it flies up into the air?</b></Default>

112
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,640
<Default><b>I'll attract its attention
and coax it to land.</b></Default>

113
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:41,799
<Default><b>Can anyone pin it down
before it starts flying again?</b></Default>

114
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,985
<Default><b>Leave it to me.</b></Default>

115
00:07:43,009 --> 00:07:44,985
<Default><b>I've got just the
Choral spell for that.</b></Default>

116
00:07:45,009 --> 00:07:46,656
<Default><b>But Wyndia and
Melty can help</b></Default>

117
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,906
<Default><b>in case I'm not able
to handle it on my own.</b></Default>

118
00:07:48,930 --> 00:07:49,930
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

119
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,156
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Can I count on you girls?</b></Default>

120
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:54,769
<Default><b>Not to worry.
The two of us have your back.</b></Default>

121
00:07:54,970 --> 00:07:56,495
<Default><b>I'm gonna
give it my all!</b></Default>

122
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,245
<Default><b>As for Raphtalia
and Eclair</b></Default>

123
00:07:58,269 --> 00:08:01,189
<Default><b>I need you to use attacks
that'll shatter his defenses.</b></Default>

124
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:02,956
<Default><b>Ren and Sadeena
can work together</b></Default>

125
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:04,545
<Default><b>to pierce the
weak scale.</b></Default>

126
00:08:04,569 --> 00:08:07,289
<Default><b>I feel that's the best
course of action we've got.</b></Default>

127
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:09,069
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

128
00:08:14,410 --> 00:08:15,886
<Default><b>You sure you're okay?</b></Default>

129
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:17,070
<Default><b>Yeah, why?</b></Default>

130
00:08:17,209 --> 00:08:19,396
<Default><b>Well, we're about to go
fight your dad.</b></Default>

131
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:21,516
<Default><b>It's gotta have you
a little worried, right?</b></Default>

132
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:22,540
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

133
00:08:22,629 --> 00:08:24,829
<Default><b>But I promise you
that I'm all right!</b></Default>

134
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:27,130
<Default><b>The reason I
came back here is</b></Default>

135
00:08:27,170 --> 00:08:29,450
<Default><b>so I can finally say
goodbye to my dad.</b></Default>

136
00:08:30,259 --> 00:08:33,639
<Default><b>Huh? Wow, you've got quite
the strong spirit, Wyndia.</b></Default>

137
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:35,950
<Default><b>You must love him.</b></Default>

138
00:08:36,179 --> 00:08:39,639
<Default><b>Aw, look at this!
You're such good little kids!</b></Default>

139
00:08:39,769 --> 00:08:41,745
<Default><b>Is now really the time
to be drinking?</b></Default>

140
00:08:41,769 --> 00:08:43,969
<Default><b>It's the perfect time
to be drinking!</b></Default>

141
00:08:44,769 --> 00:08:46,369
<Default><b>Don't you worry kids.</b></Default>

142
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,079
<Default><b>No matter what happens.</b></Default>

143
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,926
<Default><b>I swear I'll
protect you.</b></Default>

144
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:52,529
<Default><b>'Cause look at you!
You're both so adorable.</b></Default>

145
00:08:52,659 --> 00:08:54,346
<Default><b>- You're so cute!
- You reek of alcohol!</b></Default>

146
00:08:54,370 --> 00:08:57,306
<Default><b>Are you gonna be able to fight
while you're drunk, Sadeena?</b></Default>

147
00:08:57,330 --> 00:08:59,210
<Default><b>Huh? Don't
worry about me!</b></Default>

148
00:08:59,289 --> 00:09:01,830
<Default><b>I feel like the
more I drink</b></Default>

149
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:03,186
<Default><b> [groans]
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

150
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:06,340
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

151
00:09:07,299 --> 00:09:10,549
<Default><b>Grant me the power to overcome
the obstacles before me!</b></Default>

152
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,970
<Default><b>Hang on, Filo.</b></Default>

153
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:16,059
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

154
00:09:23,769 --> 00:09:25,089
<Default><b>[RAPHY] Raphy.</b></Default>

155
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,206
<Default><b>You need to go and hide
with the other kids.</b></Default>

156
00:09:27,230 --> 00:09:29,296
<Default><b>Please, Master.
Let me fight with you.</b></Default>

157
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,860
<Default><b>- Atla.
- Please.</b></Default>

158
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:32,755
<Default><b>We need you
as our last resort.</b></Default>

159
00:09:32,779 --> 00:09:35,306
<Default><b>And we can't have you
getting injured before that.</b></Default>

160
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:37,450
<Default><b>I want to have
an ace up my sleeve.</b></Default>

161
00:09:37,539 --> 00:09:38,819
<Default><b>I'm your ace?</b></Default>

162
00:09:38,909 --> 00:09:41,460
<Default><b>Fine. If it helps you</b></Default>

163
00:09:41,659 --> 00:09:42,895
<Default><b>Hey, big brother!</b></Default>

164
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:45,279
<Default><b>[ATLA] Guess what
Master Naofumi told me!</b></Default>

165
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,525
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I still don't fully understand</b></Default>

166
00:09:47,549 --> 00:09:49,485
<Default><b>the ins and outs
of Atla's power.</b></Default>

167
00:09:49,509 --> 00:09:51,829
<Default><b>So it's too risky to try
and rely on it.</b></Default>

168
00:09:52,509 --> 00:09:54,509
<Default><b>We'll end this
before sunrise.</b></Default>

169
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:56,490
<Default><b>Let's go, Raphy.</b></Default>

170
00:09:56,809 --> 00:09:58,129
<Default><b>[RAPHY] Raphy.</b></Default>

171
00:09:58,519 --> 00:10:01,230
<Default><b>Come forth!
Wrath Shield!</b></Default>

172
00:10:09,029 --> 00:10:11,029
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

173
00:10:27,090 --> 00:10:28,710
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- Raphy!</b></Default>

174
00:10:29,549 --> 00:10:31,149
<Default><b>- [straining]
- Raphy.</b></Default>

175
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,750
<Default><b>Stay back!</b></Default>

176
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,160
<Default><b>I'm all right.</b></Default>

177
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:41,480
<Default><b>There he is.</b></Default>

178
00:10:44,889 --> 00:10:46,375
<Default><b>[SADEENA, MELTY, WYNDIA]
Dragon vein</b></Default>

179
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:48,745
<Default><b>We call out so that
you may hear our wish!</b></Default>

180
00:10:48,769 --> 00:10:51,360
<Default><b>As source of thy power</b></Default>

181
00:10:51,529 --> 00:10:53,586
<Default><b>Impart to me
the laws of the nature</b></Default>

182
00:10:53,610 --> 00:10:55,086
<Default><b>and grant me
the power to</b></Default>

183
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:57,150
<Default><b>overcome the
obstacles before me!</b></Default>

184
00:10:58,159 --> 00:11:00,096
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON] If you
sacrifice yourself to me</b></Default>

185
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,306
<Default><b>Shield Hero</b></Default>

186
00:11:01,330 --> 00:11:04,289
<Default><b>then you have my word
that I will do all in my power</b></Default>

187
00:11:04,370 --> 00:11:07,130
<Default><b>to exact revenge on the
humans who made you suffer.</b></Default>

188
00:11:07,250 --> 00:11:09,130
<Default><b>[scoffs]
Don't make me laugh.</b></Default>

189
00:11:10,090 --> 00:11:11,936
<Default><b>[MELTY, WYNDIA. SADEENA]
Choral Magic!</b></Default>

190
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,379
<Default><b>Boundless Sea!</b></Default>

191
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:17,929
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

192
00:11:18,139 --> 00:11:19,219
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

193
00:11:27,269 --> 00:11:29,309
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Dragonfury Dual Blades!</b></Default>

194
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:34,046
<Default><b>And one more.</b></Default>

195
00:11:34,070 --> 00:11:35,610
<Default><b>Orca Strike!</b></Default>

196
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,280
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

197
00:11:43,539 --> 00:11:46,289
<Default><b>Not good, we need her
to keep the barrier up!</b></Default>

198
00:11:46,539 --> 00:11:48,355
<Default><b>There's no time
for weakness!</b></Default>

199
00:11:48,379 --> 00:11:50,355
<Default><b>We'll just have to
try it again!</b></Default>

200
00:11:50,379 --> 00:11:51,379
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

201
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,299
<Default><b>Eclair! Now!</b></Default>

202
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:58,799
<Default><b>Multistrike
Crumble Attack!</b></Default>

203
00:11:58,889 --> 00:12:00,115
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
If he raises his defense</b></Default>

204
00:12:00,139 --> 00:12:01,615
<Default><b>we use attacks
that scale.</b></Default>

205
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:04,319
<Default><b>If he lowers it, then we
use our strongest moves.</b></Default>

206
00:12:06,179 --> 00:12:07,559
<Default><b>We can do this!</b></Default>

207
00:12:09,269 --> 00:12:10,649
<Default><b>Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

208
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:14,940
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

209
00:12:15,149 --> 00:12:16,149
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

210
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:19,700
<Default><b>[shouting]</b></Default>

211
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:24,240
<Default><b>Now, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

212
00:12:25,539 --> 00:12:27,870
<Default><b>Life Force Blade</b></Default>

213
00:12:29,539 --> 00:12:31,960
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

214
00:12:40,090 --> 00:12:41,290
<Default><b>[straining]</b></Default>

215
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:54,269
<Default><b>Master Naofumi,
I'm sorry.</b></Default>

216
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,885
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON]
Shield Hero</b></Default>

217
00:13:02,909 --> 00:13:06,370
<Default><b>your folly demands a death
ripe with suffering!</b></Default>

218
00:13:08,789 --> 00:13:09,949
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

219
00:13:14,629 --> 00:13:16,066
<Default><b>[WYNDIA, MELTY]
Oh, tainted land</b></Default>

220
00:13:16,090 --> 00:13:19,220
<Default><b>alter the flow of your
accursed dragon vein.</b></Default>

221
00:13:20,299 --> 00:13:21,499
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

222
00:13:24,139 --> 00:13:25,220
<Default><b>Not yet.</b></Default>

223
00:13:25,470 --> 00:13:27,769
<Default><b>We still... need more.</b></Default>

224
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:32,019
<Default><b>[FOHL] Hey, Atla.</b></Default>

225
00:13:33,149 --> 00:13:35,495
<Default><b>What do we do
if their plan doesn't work?</b></Default>

226
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:37,480
<Default><b>As Master
Naofumi's servants</b></Default>

227
00:13:37,740 --> 00:13:39,586
<Default><b>we have a
duty to carry out.</b></Default>

228
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:41,426
<Default><b>In order to help
the plan succeed</b></Default>

229
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:43,450
<Default><b>we have to do
whatever it takes.</b></Default>

230
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:44,740
<Default><b>Atla...</b></Default>

231
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:49,159
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

232
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:52,199
<Default><b>[shouting]</b></Default>

233
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,590
<Default><b>[ATLA] A wall?</b></Default>

234
00:13:57,669 --> 00:13:59,259
<Default><b>I can't break it!</b></Default>

235
00:14:00,419 --> 00:14:02,549
<Default><b>[grunts] [screaming]</b></Default>

236
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:07,590
<Default><b>Big brother!</b></Default>

237
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:10,220
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

238
00:14:11,389 --> 00:14:12,440
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

239
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,519
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

240
00:14:13,690 --> 00:14:15,330
<Default><b>You've gotta break it!</b></Default>

241
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,610
<Default><b>Damn it!</b></Default>

242
00:14:24,779 --> 00:14:25,859
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

243
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,959
<Default><b>[ATLA]
This is my last attack.</b></Default>

244
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:35,590
<Default><b>Even if it costs
me my life.</b></Default>

245
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:39,129
<Default><b>I'll remove any obstacle that
stands in my Masters way.</b></Default>

246
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,720
<Default><b>After all it's my duty!</b></Default>

247
00:14:47,259 --> 00:14:51,269
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

248
00:14:51,850 --> 00:14:53,090
<Default><b>Because I...</b></Default>

249
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:57,440
<Default><b>Am Master
Naofumi's Shield!</b></Default>

250
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:03,650
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

251
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:06,820
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

252
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:10,110
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

253
00:15:13,789 --> 00:15:14,829
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

254
00:15:16,919 --> 00:15:18,239
<Default><b>You did great.</b></Default>

255
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,000
<Default><b>Thanks.</b></Default>

256
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,009
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

257
00:15:26,049 --> 00:15:27,409
<Default><b>There they are!</b></Default>

258
00:15:28,389 --> 00:15:29,589
<Default><b>[straining]</b></Default>

259
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:34,019
<Default><b>[cooing]</b></Default>

260
00:15:40,899 --> 00:15:42,505
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA, MELTY]
Filo!</b></Default>

261
00:15:42,529 --> 00:15:44,070
<Default><b>Gaelion!</b></Default>

262
00:15:44,610 --> 00:15:45,610
<Default><b>Filo!</b></Default>

263
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:47,005
<Default><b>Please wake up!</b></Default>

264
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:49,029
<Default><b>I'm begging you</b></Default>

265
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,440
<Default><b>[muttering]</b></Default>

266
00:15:52,950 --> 00:15:56,080
<Default><b>Melty's here?
And Raphtalia too?</b></Default>

267
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,645
<Default><b>Thank goodness!</b></Default>

268
00:15:57,669 --> 00:15:59,539
<Default><b>I'm so glad you're safe.</b></Default>

269
00:16:00,169 --> 00:16:01,605
<Default><b>Gaelion, you're okay!</b></Default>

270
00:16:01,629 --> 00:16:02,709
<Default><b>[cooing]</b></Default>

271
00:16:03,629 --> 00:16:05,009
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

272
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:06,660
<Default><b>[crumbling]</b></Default>

273
00:16:10,429 --> 00:16:11,429
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

274
00:16:13,519 --> 00:16:15,679
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

275
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:20,730
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

276
00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:22,390
<Default><b>[bubbling]</b></Default>

277
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:27,940
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

278
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,690
<Default><b>[splashing]</b></Default>

279
00:16:35,450 --> 00:16:36,476
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

280
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,385
<Default><b>Dad, can we
go fly over there?</b></Default>

281
00:16:38,409 --> 00:16:40,919
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

282
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,720
<Default><b>Sweet dreams, Dad.
Sleep tight, okay?</b></Default>

283
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:52,179
<Default><b>I'm... glad I got to
be your daughter.</b></Default>

284
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:53,576
<Default><b>Goodbye, Dad.</b></Default>

285
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,720
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

286
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:00,719
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

287
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:08,255
<Default><b>[SADEENA, WYNDIA, MELTY]
Hear me tainted land</b></Default>

288
00:17:08,279 --> 00:17:10,919
<Default><b>for our desires and our
wishes to save the world</b></Default>

289
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:13,029
<Default><b>are akin to a
pure stream</b></Default>

290
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:15,990
<Default><b>washing away
all hatred and anger.</b></Default>

291
00:17:16,289 --> 00:17:19,710
<Default><b>Dragon vein, we call upon thee
to grant us a miracle!</b></Default>

292
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:22,420
<Default><b>Erasing Aqua Splash!</b></Default>

293
00:17:23,289 --> 00:17:25,250
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

294
00:17:43,230 --> 00:17:44,519
<Default><b>[shouting]</b></Default>

295
00:17:46,069 --> 00:17:47,990
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

296
00:18:00,829 --> 00:18:02,309
<Default><b>Oh, no, you don't!</b></Default>

297
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:05,839
<Default><b>Air Strike Shield!
Second Shield! Dritte Shield!</b></Default>

298
00:18:06,039 --> 00:18:07,199
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

299
00:18:10,630 --> 00:18:13,009
<Default><b>Here goes.
Instant Blade, Mist!</b></Default>

300
00:18:14,549 --> 00:18:18,180
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

301
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:31,150
<Default><b>Is it all over now?</b></Default>

302
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:33,200
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

303
00:18:34,910 --> 00:18:36,070
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

304
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,560
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

305
00:18:49,339 --> 00:18:51,025
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON]
Wrath will always dwell</b></Default>

306
00:18:51,049 --> 00:18:53,130
<Default><b>within the depths
of your heart.</b></Default>

307
00:18:58,140 --> 00:19:00,180
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

308
00:19:05,059 --> 00:19:06,059
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

309
00:19:16,359 --> 00:19:17,466
<Default><b>[MAYOR]
Goodness.</b></Default>

310
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,636
<Default><b>I can't tell you just
how thankful we are</b></Default>

311
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:20,966
<Default><b>you came, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

312
00:19:20,990 --> 00:19:22,176
<Default><b>If it weren't for you</b></Default>

313
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:25,160
<Default><b>the Sword Hero would've gotten
us killed by that plague.</b></Default>

314
00:19:25,250 --> 00:19:27,730
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Don't blame Ren
for what happened.</b></Default>

315
00:19:28,089 --> 00:19:29,476
<Default><b>You're responsible.</b></Default>

316
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:30,686
<Default><b>You manipulated him</b></Default>

317
00:19:30,710 --> 00:19:33,106
<Default><b>just so you could steal
the dragon's treasure.</b></Default>

318
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:34,930
<Default><b>You got what
you deserved.</b></Default>

319
00:19:35,259 --> 00:19:36,419
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

320
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:48,079
<Default><b>Please forgive me.</b></Default>

321
00:19:49,269 --> 00:19:52,269
<Default><b>I've done something
that I can never atone for.</b></Default>

322
00:19:53,819 --> 00:19:55,499
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
I already knew.</b></Default>

323
00:19:55,569 --> 00:19:56,569
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

324
00:19:56,819 --> 00:19:58,545
<Default><b>I also knew that
the villagers had</b></Default>

325
00:19:58,569 --> 00:20:00,889
<Default><b>manipulated you to
get what they wanted.</b></Default>

326
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:03,410
<Default><b>But, I still couldn't
forgive you.</b></Default>

327
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:11,280
<Default><b>Thank you, Ren.</b></Default>

328
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:12,880
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

329
00:20:13,420 --> 00:20:15,799
<Default><b>You saved my life</b></Default>

330
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:17,220
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

331
00:20:17,549 --> 00:20:19,759
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

332
00:20:24,019 --> 00:20:25,825
<Default><b>[FATHER DRAGON ]
I must say, Shield Hero</b></Default>

333
00:20:25,849 --> 00:20:28,745
<Default><b>it's a wonderful thing to
watch one's daughter grow up.</b></Default>

334
00:20:28,769 --> 00:20:31,309
<Default><b>[gasps]
Wait that voice. No way!</b></Default>

335
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:34,126
<Default><b>[FATHER DRAGON ] It seems
this body became a vessel</b></Default>

336
00:20:34,150 --> 00:20:36,279
<Default><b>allowing me to
escape annihilation.</b></Default>

337
00:20:36,779 --> 00:20:37,795
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Huh.</b></Default>

338
00:20:37,819 --> 00:20:40,339
<Default><b>You sure you don't
wanna say anything to her?</b></Default>

339
00:20:40,609 --> 00:20:43,529
<Default><b>Not when Wyndia is trying
to overcome my death.</b></Default>

340
00:20:43,990 --> 00:20:46,870
<Default><b>I think it'd be best to
keep it a secret for her sake.</b></Default>

341
00:20:47,829 --> 00:20:48,960
<Default><b>Agreed.</b></Default>

342
00:20:49,539 --> 00:20:51,539
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

343
00:20:51,670 --> 00:20:52,870
<Default><b>- Hm?
- Huh?</b></Default>

344
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:55,850
<Default><b>Give back the experience
points you took from me!</b></Default>

345
00:20:56,339 --> 00:20:57,419
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

346
00:20:58,130 --> 00:20:59,290
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

347
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:01,906
<Default><b>Give them back!
Give them back!</b></Default>

348
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:03,759
<Default><b>Give them
back right now!</b></Default>

349
00:21:03,849 --> 00:21:06,099
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Wait, Filo's curse is gone.</b></Default>

350
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:08,930
<Default><b>Did the Emperor Dragon
absorb it?</b></Default>

351
00:21:11,230 --> 00:21:13,309
<Default><b>All's well
that ends well</b></Default>

352
00:21:14,109 --> 00:21:15,690
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

353
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,480
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

354
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:21,200
<Default><b>- [roaring]
- [whimpers]</b></Default>

355
00:21:25,450 --> 00:21:26,890
<Default><b>Let me ride, too!</b></Default>

356
00:21:32,420 --> 00:21:33,420
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

357
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:37,420
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

358
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:39,906
<Default><b>[exclaiming]</b></Default>

359
00:21:39,930 --> 00:21:41,970
<Default><b>- [FILO] Wait!
- Huh?</b></Default>

360
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:44,116
<Default><b>I'm the one
who gives Master rides!</b></Default>

361
00:21:44,140 --> 00:21:45,890
<Default><b>Me and nobody else!</b></Default>

362
00:21:46,430 --> 00:21:47,590
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

363
00:21:49,180 --> 00:21:50,616
<Default><b>Listen up Gaelion!</b></Default>

364
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:52,456
<Default><b>Grow up to be
a great dragon.</b></Default>

365
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:54,190
<Default><b>Just like my dad was</b></Default>

366
00:21:55,690 --> 00:21:57,529
<Default><b>[screeching]</b></Default>

